Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.82,0:01:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,With high hopes, humans\Nleave Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.06,0:01:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,...to begin a new life in\Nthe space colonies.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.83,0:01:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But the United Earth Sphere\NAlliance gains military power...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.73,0:01:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,...and in the name of\NJustice and Peace...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.83,0:01:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...seizes control of one\Ncolony after the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.81,0:01:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The year is After Colony 195.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.38,0:01:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Operation Meteor.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.08,0:01:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,To counter the Alliance's\Ntyranny, rebel colonists...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.62,0:01:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,...bring new arsenals\Nto the Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.08,0:01:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,...disguising them as\Nshooting stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.92,0:02:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But the Alliance headquarters\Ncatches on to this operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.20,0:02:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you, Father?!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.67,0:02:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Relena...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.21,0:02:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.37,0:02:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Your real name is\NRelena Peacecraft.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.75,0:02:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.49,0:02:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- Here she is!\N- This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.16,0:02:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Get the camera rolling!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.46,0:02:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Darlian!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.43,0:02:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Relena Darlian!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.06,0:02:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Any comments on Minister\NDarlian's assassination?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.33,0:02:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we consider this\Na declaration of war?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.13,0:02:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the start of a war?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.14,0:02:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't push! Step back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.97,0:02:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Relena!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.01,0:02:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How could they ask that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.08,0:02:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,None of them has any idea why\NFather was actually assassinated.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.27,0:03:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.24,0:03:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Relena...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.95,0:03:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.28,0:03:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't able to save Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.39,0:03:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.52,0:03:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just glad that you\Nweren't injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.62,0:03:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew something like this\Nwould happen one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.57,0:03:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Relena...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.87,0:03:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your real name is{\i0}\N{\i1}Relena Peacecraft.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.71,0:03:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're the daughter of{\i0}\N{\i1}the Peacecraft family...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.01,0:04:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...who once advocated{\i0}\N{\i1}Complete Pacifism.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.25,0:04:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he say anything\Nbefore he passed away?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.72,0:04:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No, he didn't say a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.52,0:04:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I have something to\Ntell you, Relena.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.33,0:04:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.59,0:04:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Relena?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.00,0:04:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You're my real mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.03,0:04:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll always be my mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.27,0:04:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Relena...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.31,0:04:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that Minister Darlian\Nis dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.84,0:04:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,...there are no diplomats\Nacting as a bridge...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.65,0:04:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,...between Earth and\Nthe colonies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.55,0:04:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.68,0:04:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He was quite the individual.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.22,0:04:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just the type of person who{\i0}\N{\i1}is sacrificed to a new era.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.16,0:04:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, by the way Lady Une.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.19,0:04:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not planning on\Nreturning here yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.89,0:04:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, I still have something{\i0}\N{\i1}to take care of.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.16,0:04:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I need a little more time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.97,0:04:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,To get Darlian's daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.50,0:04:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't usually make mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.34,0:05:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'd like your permission to{\i0}\N{\i1}head to the J.A.P. Point...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.64,0:05:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...with some mobile suits.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.81,0:05:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Take five mobile suits.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.68,0:05:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That many?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.05,0:05:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,A dark shadow seems to\Nfollow us wherever we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.95,0:05:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You mean the Gundams.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.35,0:05:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The Gundams have only been\Nattacking our facilities...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.96,0:05:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,...and the new type of\Nmobile suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.76,0:05:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Think of it as a precaution.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.60,0:05:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But if a Gundam should attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.00,0:05:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,...five suits might not\Nbe enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.68,0:05:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be late for the party!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.05,0:05:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.32,0:05:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Delete files on Heero Yuy\Nat the Saint Gabriel Institute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.52,0:05:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Transfer procedures complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.06,0:05:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.07,0:06:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.28,0:06:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, it's Relena!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.88,0:06:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Was her father assassinated\Nby colony terrorists?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.55,0:06:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the press is all over it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.49,0:06:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Relena!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.29,0:06:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry to hear\Nabout your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.22,0:06:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I were anywhere\Nbut at a party.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.09,0:06:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,All this festivity just\Nmakes me sadder.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.10,0:06:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's kind of you both.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.83,0:06:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't be sad forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.30,0:06:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's try our best to be stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.74,0:06:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Father wouldn't want me\Nfeeling sorry for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.07,0:06:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Relena...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.91,0:06:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Transferring?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.98,0:06:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Heero is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.18,0:06:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But he hasn't even been\Nhere for a month yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.78,0:06:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you off to fight again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.39,0:06:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's your next mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.09,0:07:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I met Dr. J.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.30,0:07:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So even you can be surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.57,0:07:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Since we met, you're the one\Nwho's always surprising me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.10,0:07:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If you killed me now it'd\Ncause quite a commotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.04,0:07:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think you want that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.41,0:07:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The school's holding a party.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.81,0:07:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Might as well enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.98,0:07:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,At least until the dance\Nis over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.53,0:07:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,They finally made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.99,0:07:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This fog would slow\Nanyone down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.70,0:07:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be moving the mobile suits\Nto the hangar at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.33,0:07:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.84,0:07:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.10,0:07:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.01,0:07:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,A Gundam!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.32,0:08:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You let the enemy penetrate\Na little too easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.32,0:08:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You can only blame yourselves\Nfor poor security.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.11,0:08:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is that dimwit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.61,0:08:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He's up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.81,0:08:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He's right over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.68,0:08:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You're late, Trowa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.05,0:08:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Why can't you just stay here\Nand wait like everyone else?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.69,0:08:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I made it here on time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.55,0:08:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.59,0:08:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.39,0:08:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We're up next!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.16,0:08:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- The audience is waiting!\N- Yeah, sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.23,0:08:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.80,0:08:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,All you have to do\Nis stand still.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.80,0:08:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ladies and Gentlemen!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.00,0:08:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Our next performance is\Nby Catherine Bloom...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.04,0:08:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,...the knife-throwing star\Nof the circus!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.34,0:09:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What a babe!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.98,0:09:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,There she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.15,0:09:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Here goes, Trowa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.87,0:09:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Go for it girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.14,0:09:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Look a little scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.14,0:09:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise I won't have\Nany fun, my little doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.44,0:09:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.92,0:09:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not afraid of anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.89,0:09:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's death...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.53,0:09:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He's begging for his death.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.73,0:09:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.60,0:09:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanna die, Trowa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:10:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.08,0:10:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,T-Trowa...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.20,0:10:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Trowa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.37,0:10:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you dodge it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.70,0:10:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not paid to dodge.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.47,0:10:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You looked just like\Na wild beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.91,0:10:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,With eyes like that lion's.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.41,0:10:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops, I guess I insulted him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.75,0:10:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd look better out there\Nif you smiled a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.38,0:10:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You're good looking, and\NI'm not just saying that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.39,0:10:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh, I forgot the most\Nimportant thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.19,0:10:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Trowa! I'm sorry I hit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.46,0:10:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, it's my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.47,0:11:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Trowa! How about that smile?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.75,0:11:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! It's Relena!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.68,0:11:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,She must be feeling better.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.38,0:11:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's a shame her dress\Nwasn't ready for the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.55,0:11:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I can imagine it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.79,0:11:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I can picture her dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.03,0:11:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Heero, I know too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.10,0:11:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You still gonna kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.57,0:11:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.14,0:11:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Before, I didn't want to die\Nwithout any answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.21,0:11:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But now it's different.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.88,0:11:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I know how you\Nfeel when you fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.31,0:11:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And now I'm fighting with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.78,0:11:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,With me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.12,0:11:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.02,0:12:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's an OZ mobile\Nsuit carrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.93,0:12:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,They've discovered this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.39,0:12:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Heero!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.67,0:12:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't stop at anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.40,0:12:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be reported as a terrorist\Nattack against the Alliance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.54,0:12:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't feel great about this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.11,0:12:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Attacking a defenseless{\i0}\N{\i1}civil facility.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.71,0:12:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Then stay behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.05,0:12:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone else can lead!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.68,0:12:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}B- But why?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.32,0:12:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That attitude risks your\Nlife and the others'!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.99,0:12:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't have that in a leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.16,0:12:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Forgive my insubordination!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.86,0:12:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll carry out the mission!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.13,0:12:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well. Get on with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.99,0:12:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Roger!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.70,0:12:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We'll descend immediately!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.73,0:12:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to relax, Lady...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.41,0:12:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.68,0:12:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Roger!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.95,0:13:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's that?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.92,0:13:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out! It's the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.32,0:13:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Has the war started?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.66,0:13:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The colony's attacking!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.76,0:13:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.89,0:13:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.36,0:13:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The military's mobile suits!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.66,0:13:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would they be\Nfighting here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.90,0:13:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Relena!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.97,0:13:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Relena!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.88,0:13:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Leo, Aries, both confirmed\Nas standard suits.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.08,0:13:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.52,0:13:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Why's the enemy out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.89,0:13:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's coming!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.68,0:14:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're fighting off an{\i0}\N{\i1}enemy mobile suit!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.25,0:14:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of suit is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.98,0:14:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have no idea!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.39,0:14:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've never seen it before!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.65,0:14:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Colonel Treize predicted this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.92,0:14:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's probably them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.79,0:14:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But why did it show up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.60,0:14:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Capture that unconfirmed suit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.60,0:14:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Dispatch the remaining\NAries suits!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.88,0:14:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.35,0:14:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Others are attacking OZ\Nfacilities besides me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.96,0:15:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I know one of them's Trowa,\Nbut are there others too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.19,0:15:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Other Gundam pilots like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.13,0:15:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Wish I could meet them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.75,0:15:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This is good stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.15,0:15:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing like a good drink\Nafter work!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.28,0:15:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You got that right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.98,0:15:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Duo! Duo!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.49,0:15:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up Duo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.72,0:15:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.76,0:15:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Just thinking how beautiful\Nthe moon looks from Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.49,0:15:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You bet; it's a beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.03,0:15:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,From the colony the moon\Nis just too close.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.70,0:15:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just like a graveyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.80,0:15:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah? A graveyard?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.27,0:15:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonder how long I'll be able\Nto see the moon like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.98,0:15:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt if that guy even\Nlooks at the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.01,0:16:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He should enjoy life, rather\Nthan trying to outsmart me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.65,0:16:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,While he's alive, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.65,0:16:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what you're saying,\Nbut it's not that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.59,0:16:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just human nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.63,0:16:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that guy doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.66,0:16:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He's unreal!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.93,0:16:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,His suit is more agile\Nthan ours could ever be!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.23,0:16:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a flight model! Ascend!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.33,0:16:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.85,0:17:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.85,0:17:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop crying and run!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.72,0:17:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.49,0:17:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be all right! Just hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.16,0:17:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We will!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.38,0:17:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Relena...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.54,0:17:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Heero?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.83,0:17:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.64,0:18:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd be better off if she died!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.38,0:18:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Why's he stopped?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.52,0:18:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.55,0:18:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The Gundam's protecting\NDarlian's daughter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.22,0:18:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes! No mistake about it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.89,0:18:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's the girl we're after;\NRelena Darlian!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.39,0:18:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What's she got to do\Nwith the Gundam's pilot?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.87,0:18:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Heero... is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.71,0:18:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.41,0:18:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Why can't I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.12,0:18:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Why can't I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.72,0:19:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,All our suits are destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.66,0:19:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Then I'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.93,0:19:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Colonel Treize is on the line!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.96,0:19:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.96,0:19:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lady Une.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.73,0:19:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cancel the mission.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.60,0:19:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Return at once.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.33,0:19:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But Colonel Treize!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.90,0:19:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've decided to let Darlian's{\i0}\N{\i1}daughter live.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.54,0:19:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?! The mission was to...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.81,0:19:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lady...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.11,0:19:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We were met by an{\i0}\N{\i1}unexpected enemy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.61,0:19:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't think of it as a failure.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.45,0:19:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come back.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.68,0:19:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.22,0:20:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thank you very much,{\i0}\N{\i1}Colonel Treize.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.53,0:20:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure Lieutenant Zechs{\i0}\N{\i1}will be pleased.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.46,0:20:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Zechs has always gone out\Nof his way to help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.70,0:20:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Saving Relena is the least I can\Ndo to thank him for his efforts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.71,0:20:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Give Lieutenant Zechs\Nmy regards.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.54,0:20:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, sir!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.45,0:20:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So the rumors were true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.28,0:20:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Zechs still has a living\Nblood relative.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.35,0:20:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He could've said something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.33,0:20:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.96,0:20:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd rather live here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.03,0:20:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Heero, that's you, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.77,0:20:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Answer me! Heero!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.31,0:20:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you rescue me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.81,0:20:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah-why did I save her?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.91,0:20:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,She knows too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.81,0:21:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you gonna kill me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.25,0:21:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me, Heero!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.38,0:21:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Heero...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.98,0:21:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,How come I can't kill her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.54,0:21:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Heero!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.48,0:22:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.65,0:22:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Heero.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.00,0:23:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Leaders of the Alliance\NMilitary gather...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.73,0:23:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,...at the New Edwards Base to\Ndiscuss armament reduction...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.44,0:23:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,...and Treize Khushrenada,\NOZ's leader...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.94,0:23:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,...skillfully lays a trap to\Nattract the Gundam pilots.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.68,0:23:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The Alliance Military is\Ndestroyed by the Gundams.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.95,0:23:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Treize's trap opens the gates\Nto a new era of bloodshed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.82,0:23:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, on Gundam Wing, Episode 7,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.00,0:23:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,"Scenario for Bloodshed".
